  20,110,JA’LEMU MA BEJNE ‘EJDIHIM WE MA HALFEHUM WE LA JUHITUNE BIHI ‘ILMÆN
  20,111,WE ‘ANETIL-WUXHUHU LILHEJJIL-KAJJUMI WE KAD HABE MEN HEMELE DHULMÆN
  20,112,WE MEN JA’MEL MINE ES-SALIHATI WE HUWE MU’UMINUN FELA JEHAFU DHULMÆN WE LA HEDMÆN
  20,113,WE KEDHELIKE ‘ENZELNAHU KUR’ANÆN ‘AREBIJÆN WE SERREFNA FIHI MINEL-WA’IDI LE’ALLEHUM JETTEKUNE ‘EW JUHDITHU LEHUM DHIKRÆN
  20,114,FETA’ALALLAHUL-MELIKUL-HEKKU WE LA TA’XHEL BIL-KUR’ANI MIN KABLI ‘EN JUKDA ‘ILEJKE WEHJUHU WE KUL RABBI ZIDNI ‘ILMÆN
  20,115,WE LEKAD ‘AHIDNA ‘ILA ‘ADEME MIN KABLU FENESIJE WE LEM NEXHID LEHU ‘AZMÆN
  20,116,WE ‘IDH KULNA LILMELA’IKETI ESXHUDU LI’DEME FESEXHEDU ‘ILLA ‘IBLISE ‘EBA
  20,117,FEKULNA JA ‘ADEMU ‘INNE HADHA ‘ADUWUN LEKE WE LIZEWXHIKE FELA JUHRIXHENNEKUMA MINEL-XHENNETI FETESHKA
  20,118,‘INNE LEKE ‘ELLA TEXHU’A FIHA WE LA TA’RA
  20,119,WE ‘ENNEKE LA TEDHME’U FIHA WE LA TEDHA
  20,120,FEWESWESE ‘ILEJHI ESH-SHEJTANU KALE JA ‘ADEMU HEL ‘EDULLUKE ‘ALA SHEXHERETIL-HULDI WE MULKIN LA JEBLA
  20,121,FE’EKELA MINHA FEBEDET LEHUMA SEW’ATUHUMA WE TEFIKA JEHSIFANI ‘ALEJHIMA MIN WEREKIL-XHENNETI WE ‘ASA ‘ADEMU REBBEHU FEGAWA
  20,122,THUMME EXHTEBAHU REBBUHU FETABE ‘ALEJHI WE HEDA
  20,123,KALE EHBITA MINHA XHEMI’ÆN BA’DUKUM LIBA’DIN ‘ADUWUN FE’IMMA JE’TIJENNEKUM MINNI HUDEN FEMENI ETTEBE’A HUDAJE FELA JEDILLU WE LA JESHKA
  20,124,WE MEN ‘A’REDE ‘AN DHIKRI FE’INNE LEHU MA’ISHETEN DENKÆN WE NEHSHURUHU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘A’MA
  20,125,KALE RABBI LIME HESHERTENI ‘A’MA WE KAD KUNTU BESIRÆN
  20,126,KALE KEDHALIKE ‘ETETKE ‘AJATUNA FENESITEHA WE KEDHELIKEL-JEWME TUNSA
  20,127,WE KEDHELIKE NEXHZI MEN ‘ESREFE WE LEM JU’UMIN BI’AJATI RABBIHI WE LE’ADHABUL-’AHIRETI ‘ESHEDDU WE ‘EBKA
  20,128,‘EFELEM JEHDI LEHUM KEM ‘EHLEKNA KABLEHUM MINEL-KURUNI JEMSHUNE FI MESAKINIHIM ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LI’WLI EN-NUHA
  20,129,WE LEWLA KELIMETUN SEBEKAT MIN RABBIKE LEKANE LIZAMÆN WE ‘EXHELUN MUSEMMEN
  20,130,FASBIR ‘ALA MA JEKULUNE WE SEBBIH BIHEMDI RABBIKE KABLE TULU’I ESH-SHEMSI WE KABLE GURUBIHA WE MIN ‘ANA’IL-LEJLI FESEBBIH WE ‘ETRAFE EN-NEHARI LE’ALLEKE TERDA
  20,131,WE LA TEMUDDENNE ‘AJNEJKE ‘ILA MA METTA’NA BIHI ‘EZWAXHÆN MINHUM ZEHRETEL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA LINEFTINEHUM FIHI WE RIZKU RABBIKE HAJRUN WE ‘EBKA
  20,132,WE ‘MUR ‘EHLEKE BIS-SELÆTI WE ESTEBIR ‘ALEJHA LA NES’ELUKE RIZKÆN NEHNU NERZUKUKE WEL-’AKIBETU LILTTEKWA
  20,133,WE KALU LEWLA JE’TINA BI’AJETIN MIN RABBIHI ‘EWELEM TE’TIHIM BEJJINETU MA FI ES-SUHUFIL-’ULA
  20,134,WE LEW ‘ENNA ‘EHLEKNAHUM BI’ADHABIN MIN KABLIHI LEKALU REBBENA LEWLA ‘ERSELTE ‘ILEJNA RESULÆN FENETTEBI’A ‘AJATIKE MIN KABLI ‘EN NEDHILLE WE NEHZA
  20,135,KUL KULLUN MUTEREBBISUN FETEREBBESU FESETA’LEMUNE MEN ‘ESHABU ES-SIRATI ES-SEWIJI WE MENI EHTEDA
  21,1,EKTEREBE LILNNASI HISABUHUM WE HUM FI GAFLETIN MU’RIDUNE
  21,2,MA JE’TIHIM MIN DHIKRIN MIN RABBIHIM MUHDETHIN ‘ILLA ESTEMA’UHU WE HUM JEL’ABUNE
  21,3,LAHIJETEN KULUBUHUM WE ‘ESERRU EN-NEXHWAL-LEDHINE DHELEMU HEL HADHA ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUKUM ‘EFETE’TUNE ES-SIHRE WE ‘ENTUM TUBSIRUNE
  21,4,KALE RABBI JA’LEMUL-KAWLE FI ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI WE HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  21,5,BEL KALU ‘EDGATHU ‘EHLAMIN BEL EFTERAHU BEL HUWE SHA’IRUN FELJE’TINA BI’AJETIN KEMA ‘URSILEL-’EWWELUNE
  21,6,MA ‘AMENET KABLEHUM MIN KARJETIN ‘EHLEKNAHA ‘EFEHUM JU’UMINUNE
  21,7,WE MA ‘ERSELNA KABLEKE ‘ILLA RIXHALÆN NUHI ‘ILEJHIM FAS’ELU ‘EHLE EDH-DHIKRI ‘IN KUNTUM LA TA’LEMUNE
  21,8,WE MA XHE’ALNAHUM XHESEDÆN LA JE’KULUNET-TA’AME WE MA KANU HALIDINE
  21,9,THUMME SEDEKNAHUMUL-WA’DE FE’ENXHEJNAHUM WE MEN NESHA’U WE ‘EHLEKNAL-MUSRIFINE
  21,10,LEKAD ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKUM KITABÆN FIHI DHIKRUKUM ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  21,11,WE KEM KASEMNA MIN KARJETIN KANET DHALIMETEN WE ‘ENSHE’NA BA’DEHA KAWMÆN ‘AHARINE
  21,12,FELEMMA ‘EHESSU BE’SENA ‘IDHA HUM MINHA JERKUDUNE
  21,13,LA TERKUDU WE ERXHI’U ‘ILA MA ‘UTRIFTUM FIHI WE MESAKINIKUM LE’ALLEKUM TUS’ELUNE
  21,14,KALU JA WEJLENA ‘INNA KUNNA DHALIMINE
  21,15,FEMA ZALET TILKE DA’WAHUM HETTA XHE’ALNAHUM HESIDÆN HAMIDINE
  21,16,WE MA HALEKNA ES-SEMA’E WEL-’ERDE WE MA BEJNEHUMA LA’IBINE
  21,17,LEW ‘EREDNA ‘EN NETTEHIDHE LEHWEN LATTEHADHNAHU MIN LEDUNNA ‘IN KUNNA FA’ILINE
  21,18,BEL NEKDHIFU BIL-HEKKI ‘ALEL-BATILI FEJEDMEGUHU FE’IDHA HUWE ZAHIKUN WE LEKUMUL-WEJLU MIMMA TESIFUNE
  21,19,WE LEHU MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MEN ‘INDEHU LA JESTEKBIRUNE ‘AN ‘IBADETIHI WE LA JESTEHSIRUNE
  21,20,JUSEBBIHUNEL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHARE LA JEFTURUNE
  21,21,‘EM ETTEHADHU ‘ALIHETEN MINEL-’ERDI HUM JUNSHIRUNE
  21,22,LEW KANE FIHIMA ‘ALIHETUN ‘ILLALLAHU LEFESEDETA FESUBHANEL-LAHI RABBIL-’ARSHI ‘AMMA JESIFUNE
  21,23,LA JUS’ELU ‘AMMA JEF’ALU WE HUM JUS’ELUNE
  21,24,‘EM ETTEHADHU MIN DUNIHI ‘ALIHETEN KUL HATU BURHANEKUM HADHA DHIKRU MEN MA’IJE WE DHIKRU MEN KABLI BEL ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’LEMUNEL-HEKKA FEHUM MU’RIDUNE
  21,25,WE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE MIN RESUL IN’ILLA NUHI ‘ILEJHI ‘ENNEHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA ‘ENA FA’BUDUNI
  21,26,WE KALU ETTEHADHE ER-REHMANU WELEDÆN SUBHANEHU BEL ‘IBADUN MUKREMUNE
  21,27,LA JESBIKUNEHU BIL-KAWLI WE HUM BI’EMRIHI JA’MELUNE
  21,28,JA’LEMU MA BEJNE ‘EJDIHIM WE MA HALFEHUM WE LA JESHFA’UNE ‘ILLA LIMENI ERTEDA WE HUM MIN HASHJETIHI MUSHFIKUNE
  21,29,WE MEN JEKUL MINHUM ‘INNI ‘ILEHUN MIN DUNIHI FEDHALIKE NEXHZIHI XHEHENNEME KEDHALIKE NEXHZI EDH-DHALIMINE
  21,30,‘EWELEM JERAL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ENNE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE KANETA RETKÆN FEFETEKNAHUMA WE XHE’ALNA MINEL-MA’I KULLE SHEJ’IN HEJJIN ‘EFELA JU’UMINUNE
  21,31,WE XHE’ALNA FIL-’ERDI REWASIJE ‘EN TEMIDE BIHIM WE XHE’ALNA FIHA FIXHAXHÆN SUBULÆN LE’ALLEHUM JEHTEDUNE
  21,32,WE XHE’ALNA ES-SEMA’E SEKFÆN MEHFUDHÆN WE HUM ‘AN ‘AJATIHA MU’RIDUNE
  21,33,WE HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKAL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHARE WE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE KULLUN FI FELEKIN JESBEHUNE
  21,34,WE MA XHE’ALNA LIBESHERIN MIN KABLIKEL-HULDE ‘EFE’IN MITTE FEHUMUL-HALIDUNE
  21,35,KULLU NEFSIN DHA’IKATUL-MEWTI WE NEBLUKUM BISH-SHERRI WEL-HAJRI FITNETEN WE ‘ILEJNA TURXHA’UNE
  21,36,WE ‘IDHA RE’AKEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘IN JETTEHIDHUNEKE ‘ILLA HUZUEN ‘EHEDHAL-LEDHI JEDHKURU ‘ALIHETEKUM WE HUM BIDHIKRI ER-REHMANI HUM KAFIRUNE
  21,37,HULIKAL-’INSANU MIN ‘AXHELIN SE’URIKUM ‘AJATI FELA TESTA’XHILUNI
  21,38,WE JEKULUNE META HADHAL-WA’DU ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  21,39,LEW JA’LEMUL-LEDHINE KEFERU HINE LA JEKUFFUNE ‘AN WUXHUHIHIMU EN-NARE WE LA ‘AN DHUHURIHIM WE LA HUM JUNSERUNE
  21,40,BEL TE’TIHIM BEGTETEN FETEBHETUHUM FELA JESTETI’UNE REDDEHA WE LA HUM JUNDHERUNE
  21,41,WE LEKADI ESTUHZI’E BIRUSULIN MIN KABLIKE FEHAKA BIEL-LEDHINE SEHIRU MINHUM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  21,42,KUL MEN JEKLE’UUKUM BIL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI MINE ER-REHMANI BEL HUM ‘AN DHIKRI RABBIHIM MU’RIDUNE
  21,43,‘EM LEHUM ‘ALIHETUN TEMNA’UHUM MIN DUNINA LA JESTETI’UNE NESRE ‘ENFUSIHIM WE LA HUM MINNA JUSHEBUNE
  21,44,BEL METTA’NA HA’UULA’ WE ‘ABA’EHUM HETTA TALE ‘ALEJHIMUL-’UMURU ‘EFELA JEREWNE ‘ENNA NE’TIL-’ERDE NENKUSUHA MIN ‘ETRAFIHA ‘EFEHUMUL-GALIBUNE
  21,45,KUL ‘INNEMA ‘UNDHIRUKUM BIL-WEHJI WE LA JESMA’U ES-SUMMU ED-DU’A’E ‘IDHA MA JUNDHERUNE
  21,46,WE LE’IN MESSET/HUM NEFHETUN MIN ‘ADHABI RABBIKE LEJEKULUNNE JA WEJLENA ‘INNA KUNNA DHALIMINE
  21,47,WE NEDA’UL-MEWAZINEL-KISTE LIJEWMIL-KIJAMETI FELA TUDHLEMU NEFSUN SHEJ’ÆN WE ‘IN KANE MITHKALE HEBBETIN MIN HARDELIN ‘ETEJNA BIHA WE KEFA BINA HASIBINE
  21,48,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA MUSA WE HARUNEL-FURKANE WE DIJA’EN WE DHIKRÆN LILMUTTEKINE
  21,49,EL-LEDHINE JEHSHEWNE REBBEHUM BIL-GAJBI WE HUM MINE ES-SA’ATI MUSHFIKUNE
  21,50,WE HEDHA DHIKRUN MUBAREKUN ‘ENZELNAHU ‘EFE’ENTUM LEHU MUNKIRUNE
  21,51,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA ‘IBRAHIME RUSHDEHU MIN KABLU WE KUNNA BIHI ‘ALIMINE
  21,52,‘IDH KALE LI’EBIHI WE KAWMIHI MA HEDHIHIT-TEMATHILU ELLETI ‘ENTUM LEHA ‘AKIFUNE
  21,53,KALU WEXHEDNA ‘ABA’ENA LEHA ‘ABIDINE
  21,54,KALE LEKAD KUNTUM ‘ENTUM WE ‘ABA’UUKUM FI DELALIN MUBININ
  21,55,KALU ‘EXHI’TENA BIL-HEKKI ‘EM ‘ENTE MINEL-LA’IBINE
  21,56,KALE BEL REBBUKUM REBBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDIL-LEDHI FETEREHUNNE WE ‘ENA ‘ALA DHALIKUM MINE ESH-SHAHIDINE
  21,57,WE TALLLEHI LE’EKIDENNE ‘ESNAMEKUM BA’DE ‘EN TUWELLU MUDBIRINE
  21,58,FEXHE’ALEHUM XHUDHADHÆN ‘ILLA KEBIRÆN LEHUM LE’ALLEHUM ‘ILEJHI JERXHI’UNE
  21,59,KALU MEN FE’ALE HADHA BI’ALIHETINA ‘INNEHU LEMINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  21,60,KALU SEMI’NA FETEN JEDHKURUHUM JUKALU LEHU ‘IBRAHIMU
  21,61,KALU FE’TU BIHI ‘ALA ‘A’JUNI EN-NASI LE’ALLEHUM JESH/HEDUNE
  21,62,KALU ‘E’ENTE FE’ALTE HADHA BI’ALIHETINA JA ‘IBRAHIMU
  21,63,KALE BEL FE’ALEHU KEBIRUHUM HADHA FAS’ELUHUM ‘IN KANU JENTIKUNE
  21,64,FEREXHA’U ‘ILA ‘ENFUSIHIM FEKALU ‘INNEKUM ‘ENTUMU EDH-DHALIMUNE
  21,65,THUMME NUKISU ‘ALA RU’USIHIM LEKAD ‘ALIMTE MA HA’UULA’ JENTIKUNE
  21,66,KALE ‘EFETA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JENFA’UKUM SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JEDURRUKUM
  21,67,‘UFFIN LEKUM WE LIMA TA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  21,68,KALU HERRIKUHU WE ENSURU ‘ALIHETEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM FA’ILINE
  21,69,KULNA JA NARU KUNI BERDÆN WE SELAMÆN ‘ALA ‘IBRAHIME
  21,70,WE ‘ERADU BIHI KEJDÆN FEXHE’ALNAHUMUL-’EHSERINE
  21,71,WE NEXHXHEJNAHU WE LUTÆN ‘ILAL-’ERDI ELLETI BAREKNA FIHA LIL’ALEMINE
  21,72,WE WEHEBNA LEHU ‘ISHAKA WE JA’KUBE NAFILETEN WE KULLÆN XHE’ALNA SALIHINE
  21,73,WE XHE’ALNAHUM ‘E’IMMETEN JEHDUNE BI’EMRINA WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJHIM FI’LEL-HAJRATI WE ‘IKAME ES-SELÆTI WE ‘ITA’E EZ-ZEKÆTI WE KANU LENA ‘ABIDINE
  21,74,WE LUTÆN ‘ATEJNAHU HUKMÆN WE ‘ILMÆN WE NEXHXHEJNAHU MINEL-KARJETI ELLETI KANET TA’MELUL-HABA’ITHE ‘INNEHUM KANU KAWME SEW’IN FASIKINE
  21,75,WE ‘EDHALNAHU FI REHMETINA ‘INNEHU MINE ES-SALIHINE
  21,76,WE NUHÆN ‘IDH NADA MIN KABLU FASTEXHEBNA LEHU FENEXHXHEJNAHU WE ‘EHLEHU MINEL-KERBIL-’ADHIMI
  21,77,WE NESERNAHU MINEL-KAWMIL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA ‘INNEHUM KANU KAWME SEW’IN FE’EGREKNAHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  21,78,WE DAWUDE WE SULEJMANE ‘IDH JEHKUMANI FIL-HERTHI ‘IDH NEFESHET FIHI GANEMUL-KAWMI WE KUNNA LIHUKMIHIM SHAHIDINE
  21,79,FEFEHHEMNAHA SULEJMANE WE KULLÆN ‘ATEJNA HUKMÆN WE ‘ILMÆN WE SEHHARNA ME’A DAWUDEL-XHIBALE JUSEBBIHNE WET-TEJRE WE KUNNA FA’ILINE
  21,80,WE ‘ALLEMNAHU SEN’ATE LEBUSIN LEKUM LITUHSINEKUM MIN BE’SIKUM FEHEL ‘ENTUM SHAKIRUNE
  21,81,WE LISULEJMANE ER-RIHE ‘ASIFETEN TEXHRI BI’EMRIHI ‘ILAL-’ERDI ELLETI BAREKNA FIHA WE KUNNA BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMINE
  21,82,WE MINE ESH-SHEJATINI MEN JEGUSUNE LEHU WE JA’MELUNE ‘AMELÆN DUNE DHALIKE WE KUNNA LEHUM HAFIDHINE
  21,83,WE ‘EJJUBE ‘IDH NADA REBBEHU ‘ENNI MESSENI ED-DURRU WE ‘ENTE ‘ERHEMU ER-RAHIMINE
  21,84,FASTEXHEBNA LEHU FEKESHEFNA MA BIHI MIN DURRIN WE ‘ATEJNAHU ‘EHLEHU WE MITHLEHUM ME’AHUM REHMETEN MIN ‘INDINA WE DHIKRA LIL’ABIDINE
  21,85,WE ‘ISMA’ILE WE ‘IDRISE WE DHAL-KIFLI KULLUN MINE ES-SABIRINE
  21,86,WE ‘EDHALNAHUM FI REHMETINA ‘INNEHUM MINE ES-SALIHINE
  21,87,WE DHA EN-NUNI ‘IDH DHEHEBE MUGADIBÆN FEDHENNE ‘EN LEN NEKDIRE ‘ALEJHI FENADA FI EDH-DHULUMATI ‘EN LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA ‘ENTE SUBHANEKE ‘INNI KUNTU MINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  21,88,FASTEXHEBNA LEHU WE NEXHXHEJNAHU MINEL-GAMMI WE KEDHELIKE NUNXHIL-MU’UMININE
  21,89,WE ZEKERIJA ‘IDH NADA REBBEHU RABBI LA TEDHERNI FERDÆN WE ‘ENTE HAJRUL-WARITHINE
  21,90,FASTEXHEBNA LEHU WE WEHEBNA LEHU JEHJA WE ‘ESLEHNA LEHU ZEWXHEHU ‘INNEHUM KANU JUSARI’UNE FIL-HAJRATI WE JED’UNENA REGABÆN WE REHEBÆN WE KANU LENA HASHI’INE
  21,91,WE E-ETI ‘EHSENET FERXHEHA FENEFEHNA FIHA MIN RUHINA WE XHE’ALNAHA WE EBNEHA ‘AJETEN LIL’ALEMINE
  21,92,‘INNE HEDHIHI ‘UMMETUKUM ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN WE ‘ENA REBBUKUM FA’BUDUNI
  21,93,WE TEKATTA’U ‘EMREHUM BEJNEHUM KULLUN ‘ILEJNA RAXHI’UNE
  21,94,FEMEN JA’MEL MINE ES-SALIHATI WE HUWE MU’UMINUN FELA KUFRANE LISA’JIHI WE ‘INNA LEHU KATIBUNE
  21,95,WE HERAMUN ‘ALA KARJETIN ‘EHLEKNAHA ‘ENNEHUM LA JERXHI’UNE
  21,96,HETTA ‘IDHA FUTIHET JE’XHUXHU WE ME’XHUXHU WE HUM MIN KULLI HEDEBIN JENSILUNE
  21,97,WAKTEREBEL-WA’DUL-HEKKU FE’IDHA HIJE SHAHISETUN ‘EBSARUL-LEDHINE KEFERU JA WEJLENA KAD KUNNA FI GAFLETIN MIN HADHA BEL KUNNA DHALIMINE
  21,98,‘INNEKUM WE MA TA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI HESEBU XHEHENNEME ‘ENTUM LEHA WE ERIDUNE
  21,99,LEW KANE HA’UULA’ ‘ALIHETEN MA WEREDUHA WE KULLUN FIHA HALIDUNE
  21,100,LEHUM FIHA ZEFIRUN WE HUM FIHA LA JESMA’UNE
  21,101,‘INNEL-LEDHINE SEBEKAT LEHUM MINNAL-HUSNA ‘ULA’IKE ‘ANHA MUB’ADUNE
  21,102,LA JESMA’UNE HESISEHA WE HUM FI MA ESHTEHET ‘ENFUSUHUM HALIDUNE
  21,103,LA JEHZUNUHUMUL-FEZA’UL-’EKBERU WE TETELEKKAHUMUL-MELA’IKETU HADHA JEWMUKUMUL-LEDHI KUNTUM TU’ADUNE
  21,104,JEWME NETWI ES-SEMA’E KETEJJI ES-SIXHILLI LILKUTUBI KEMA BEDE’NA ‘EWWELE HALKIN NU’IDUHU WA’DÆN ‘ALEJNA ‘INNA KUNNA FA’ILINE
  21,105,WE LEKAD KETEBNA FI EZ-ZEBURI MIN BA’DI EDH-DHIKRI ‘ENNEL-’ERDE JERITHUHA ‘IBADIJE ES-SALIHUNE
  21,106,‘INNE FI HADHA LEBELAGÆN LIKAWMIN ‘ABIDINE
  21,107,WE MA ‘ERSELNAKE ‘ILLA REHMETEN LIL’ALEMINE
  21,108,KUL ‘INNEMA JUHA ‘ILEJJE ‘ENNEMA ‘ILEHUKUM ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN FEHEL ‘ENTUM MUSLIMUNE
  21,109,FE’IN TEWELLEW FEKUL ‘ADHENTUKUM ‘ALA SEWA’IN WE ‘IN ‘EDRI ‘EKARIBUN ‘EM BA’IDUN MA TU’ADUNE
  21,110,‘INNEHU JA’LEMUL-XHEHRE MINEL-KAWLI WE JA’LEMU MA TEKTUMUNE
  21,111,WE ‘IN ‘EDRI LE’ALLEHU FITNETUN LEKUM WE META’UN ‘ILA HININ
  21,112,KALE RABBI EHKUM BIL-HEKKI WE REBBUNA ER-REHMANUL-MUSTA’ANU ‘ALA MA TESIFUNE
  22,1,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ETTEKU REBBEKUM ‘INNE ZELZELETE ES-SA’ATI SHEJ’UN ‘ADHIMUN
  22,2,JEWME TEREWNEHA TEDH/HELU KULLU MURDI’ATIN ‘AMMA ‘ERDE’AT WE TEDA’U KULLU DHATI HEMLIN HEMLEHA WE TERA EN-NASE SUKARA WE MA HUM BISUKARA WE LEKINNE ‘ADHABEL-LAHI SHEDIDUN
  22,3,WE MINE EN-NASI MEN JUXHADILU FI ELLAHI BIGAJRI ‘ILMIN WE JETTEBI’U KULLE SHEJTANIN MERIDIN
  22,4,KUTIBE ‘ALEJHI ‘ENNEHU MEN TEWELLAHU FE’ENNEHU JUDILLUHU WE JEHDIHI ‘ILA ‘ADHABI ES-SA’IRI
  22,5,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘IN KUNTUM FI REJBIN MINEL-BA’THI FE’INNA HALEKNAKUM MIN TURABIN THUMME MIN NUTFETIN THUMME MIN ‘ALEKATIN THUMME MIN MUDGATIN MUHALLEKATIN WE GAJRI MUHALLEKATIN LINUBEJJINE LEKUM WE NUKIRRU FIL-’ERHAMI MA NESHA’U ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN
  22,6,DHALIKE BI’ENNEL-LAHE HUWEL-HEKKU WE ‘ENNEHU JUHJIL-MEWTA WE ‘ENNEHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  22,7,WE ‘ENNE ES-SA’ATE ‘ATIJETUN LA REJBE FIHA WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE JEB’ATHU MEN FIL-KUBURI
  22,8,WE MINE EN-NASI MEN JUXHADILU FI ELLAHI BIGAJRI ‘ILMIN WE LA HUDEN WE LA KITABIN MUNIRIN
  22,9,THANIJE ‘ITFIHI LIJUDILLE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI LEHU FI ED-DUNJA HIZJUN WE NUDHIKUHU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘ADHABEL-HERIKI
  22,10,DHALIKE BIMA KADDEMET JEDAKE WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LEJSE BIDHELLAMIN LIL’ABIDI
  22,11,WE MINE EN-NASI MEN JA’BUDU ELLAHE ‘ALA HERFIN FE’IN ‘ESABEHU HAJRUN ETME’ENNE BIHI WE ‘IN ‘ESABET/HU FITNETUN ENKALEBE ‘ALA WEXHHIHI HASIRE ED-DUNJA WEL-’AHIRETE DHALIKE HUWEL-HUSRANUL-MUBINU
  22,12,JED’U MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JEDURRUHU WE MA LA JENFA’UHU DHALIKE HUWE ED-DELALUL-BA’IDU
  22,13,JED’U LEMEN DERRUHU ‘EKREBU MIN NEF’IHI LEBI’SEL-MEWLA WE LEBI’SEL-’ASHIRU
  22,14,‘INNALL-LLAHE JUDHILUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU ‘INNALL-LLAHE JEF’ALU MA JURIDU
  22,15,MEN KANE JEDHUNNU ‘EN LEN JENSUREHU ELLAHU FI ED-DUNJA WEL-’AHIRETI FELJEMDUD BISEBEBIN ‘ILA ES-SEMA’I THUMME LIJEKTA’ FELJENDHUR HEL JUDH/HIBENNE KEJDUHU MA JEGIDHU
  22,16,WE KEDHELIKE ‘ENZELNAHU ‘AJATIN BEJJINATIN WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE JEHDI MEN JURIDU
  22,17,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WEL-LEDHINE HADU WE ES-SABI’INE WE EN-NESARA WEL-MEXHUSE WEL-LEDHINE ‘ESHREKU ‘INNALL-LLAHE JEFSILU BEJNEHUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN SHEHIDUN
  22,18,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE JESXHUDU LEHU MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MEN FIL-’ERDI WE ESH-SHEMSU WEL-KAMERU WE EN-NUXHUMU WEL-XHIBALU WE ESH-SHEXHERU WE ED-DEWABBU WE KETHIRUN MINE EN-NASI WE KETHIRUN HEKKA ‘ALEJHIL-’ADHABU WE MEN JUHINI ELLAHU FEMA LEHU MIN MUKRIM
  22,19,HEDHANI HASMANI EHTESEMU FI RABBIHIM FE-EL-LEDHINE KEFERU KUTTI’AT LEHUM THIJABUN MIN NARIN JUSEBBU MIN FEWKI RU’USIHIMUL-HEMIMU
  22,20,JUSHERU BIHI MA FI BUTUNIHIM WEL-XHULUDU
  22,21,WE LEHUM MEKAMI’U MIN HEDIDIN
  22,22,KULLEMA ‘ERADU ‘EN JEHRUXHU MINHA MIN GAMMIN ‘U’IDU FIHA WE DHUKU ‘ADHABEL-HERIKI
  22,23,‘INNALL-LLAHE JUDHILUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU JUHELLEWNE FIHA MIN ‘ESAWIRE MIN DHEHEBIN WE LU’ULU’UÆN WE LIBASUHUM FIHA HERIRUN
  22,24,WE HUDU ‘ILAT-TEJJIBI MINEL-KAWLI WE HUDU ‘ILA SIRATIL-HEMIDI
  22,25,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE JESUDDUNE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WEL-MESXHIDIL-HERAMIL-LEDHI XHE’ALNAHU LILNNASI SEWA’ENL-’AKIFU FIHI WEL-BADI WE MEN JURID FIHI BI’ILHADIN BIDHULMIN NUDHIKHU MIN ‘ADHABIN ‘ELIMIN
  22,26,WE ‘IDH BEWWE’NA LI’IBRAHIME MEKANEL-BEJTI ‘EN LA TUSHRIK BI SHEJ’ÆN WE TEHHIR BEJTIJE LILTTA’IFINE WEL-KA’IMINE WE ER-RUKKA’I ES-SUXHUDI
  22,27,WE ‘EDHDHIN FI EN-NASI BIL-HEXHXHI JE’TUKE RIXHALÆN WE ‘ALA KULLI DAMIRIN JE’TINE MIN KULLI FEXHXHIN ‘AMIKIN
  22,28,LIJESH/HEDU MENAFI’A LEHUM WE JEDHKURU ESMEL-LAHI FI ‘EJJAMIN MA’LUMATIN ‘ALA MA REZEKAHUM MIN BEHIMETIL-’EN’AM FEKULU MINHA WE ‘ET’IMUL-BA’ISEL-FEKIRE
  22,29,THUMME LIJEKDU TEFETHEHUM WE LIUFU NUDHUREHUM WE LIETTEWWEFU BIL-BEJTIL-’ATIKI
  22,30,DHALIKE WE MEN JU’ADHDHIM HURUMATI ELLAHI FEHUWE HAJRUN LEHU ‘INDE RABBIHI WE ‘UHILLET LEKUMUL-’EN’AM ‘ILLA MA JUTLA ‘ALEJKUM FAXHTENIBU ER-RIXHSE MINEL-’EWTHANI WE EXHTENIBU KAWLE EZ-ZURI
  22,31,HUNEFA’E LILLAHI GAJRE MUSHRIKINE BIHI WE MEN JUSHRIK BILLAHI FEKE’ENNEMA HARRE MINE ES-SEMA’I FETEHTEFUHUT-TEJRU ‘EW TEHWI BIHI ER-RIHU FI MEKANIN SEHIKIN
  22,32,DHALIKE WE MEN JU’ADHDHIM SHA’A’IREL-LAHI FE’INNEHA MIN TEKWAL-KULUBI
  22,33,LEKUM FIHA MENAFI’U ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN THUMME MEHILLUHA ‘ILAL-BEJTIL-’ATIKI
  22,34,WE LIKULLI ‘UMMETIN XHE’ALNA MENSEKÆN LIJEDHKURU ESMEL-LAHI ‘ALA MA REZEKAHUM MIN BEHIMETIL-’EN’AMI FE’ILEHUKUM ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN FELEHU ‘ESLIMU WE BESHSHIRIL-MUHBITINE
  22,35,EL-LEDHINE ‘IDHA DHUKIREL-LAHU WEXHILET KULUBUHUM WE ES-SABIRINE ‘ALA MA ‘ESABEHUM WEL-MUKIMI ES-SELÆTI WE MIMMA REZEKNAHUM JUNFIKUNE
  22,36,WEL-BUDNE XHE’ALNAHA LEKUM MIN SHA’A’IRI ELLAHI LEKUM FIHA HAJRUN FADHKURU ESMEL-LAHI ‘ALEJHA SEWAFFE FE’IDHA WEXHEBET XHUNUBUHA FEKULU MINHA WE ‘ET’IMUL-KANI’A WEL-MU’TERRE KEDHALIKE SEHHARNAHA LEKUM LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  22,37,LEN JENALEL-LAHE LUHUMUHA WE LA DIMA’UUHA WE LEKIN JENALUHUT-TEKWA MINKUM KEDHALIKE SEHHAREHA LEKUM LITUKEBBIRU ELLAHE ‘ALA MA HEDAKUM WE BESHSHIRIL-MUHSININE
  22,38,‘INNALL-LLAHE JUDAFI’U ‘ANIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUHIBBU KULLE HAWWANIN KEFURIN
  22,39,‘UDHINE LILLEDHINE JUKATELUNE BI’ENNEHUM DHULIMU WE ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA NESRIHIM LEKADIRUN
  22,40,EL-LEDHINE ‘UHRIXHU MIN DIJARIHIM BIGAJRI HEKKIN ‘ILLA ‘EN JEKULU REBBUNALLAHU WE LEWLA DEF’U ELLAHI EN-NASE BA’DEHUM BIBA’DIN LEHUDDIMET SEWAMI’U WE BIJA’UN WE SELEWATUN WE MESAXHIDU JUDHKERU FIHA ESMU ELLAHI KETHIRÆN WE LEJENSURENNEL-LAHU MEN JENSURUHU
  22,41,EL-LEDHINE ‘IN MEKKENNAHUM FIL-’ERDI ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ATEW EZ-ZEKÆTE WE ‘EMERU BIL-MA’RUFI WE NEHEW ‘ANIL-MUNKERI WE LILLEHI ‘AKIBETUL-’UMURI
  22,42,WE ‘IN JUKEDHDHIBUKE FEKAD KEDHDHEBET KABLEHUM KAWMU NUHIN WE ‘ADUN WE THEMUDU
  22,43,WE KAWMU ‘IBRAHIME WE KAWMU LUTIN
  22,44,WE ‘ESHABU MEDJENE WE KUDHDHIBE MUSA FE’EMLEJTU LILKAFIRINE THUMME ‘EHADHTUHUM FEKEJFE KANE NEKIRI
  22,45,FEKE’EJJIN MIN KARJETIN ‘EHLEKNAHA WE HIJE DHALIMETUN FEHIJE HAWIJETUN ‘ALA ‘URUSHIHA WE BI’RIN MU’ATTELETIN WE KASRIN MESHIDIN
  22,46,‘EFELEM JESIRU FIL-’ERDI FETEKUNE LEHUM KULUBUN JA’KILUNE BIHA ‘EW ‘ADHANUN JESMA’UNE BIHA FE’INNEHA LA TA’MAL-’EBSARU WE LEKIN TA’MAL-KULUBU ELLETI FI ES-SUDURI
  22,47,WE JESTA’XHILUNEKE BIL-’ADHABI WE LEN JUHLIFEL-LAHU WA’DEHU WE ‘INNE JEWMÆN ‘INDE RABBIKE KE’ELFI SENETIN MIMMA TA’UDDUNE
  22,48,WE KE’EJJIN MIN KARJETIN ‘EMLEJTU LEHA WE HIJE DHALIMETUN THUMME ‘EHADHTUHA WE ‘ILEJJEL-MESIRU
  22,49,KUL JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘INNEMA ‘ENA LEKUM NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  22,50,FE-EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE RIZKUN KERIMUN
  22,51,WEL-LEDHINE SE’AW FI ‘AJATINA MU’AXHIZINE ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABUL-XHEHIMI
  22,52,WE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE MIN RESULIN WE LA NEBIJIN ‘ILLA ‘IDHA TEMENNA ‘ELKA ESH-SHEJTANU FI ‘UMNIJETIHI FEJENSEHU ELLAHU MA JULKI ESH-SHEJTANU THUMME JUHKIMU ELLAHU ‘AJATIHI WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN HEKIMUN
  22,53,LIJEXH’ALE MA JULKI ESH-SHEJTANU FITNETEN LILLEDHINE FI KULUBIHIM MEREDUN WEL-KASIJETI KULUBUHUM WE ‘INNE EDH-DHALIMINE LEFI SHIKAKIN BA’IDIN
  22,54,WE LIJA’LEMEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-’ILME ‘ENNEHUL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKE FEJU’UMINU BIHI FETUHBITE LEHU KULUBUHUM WE ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEHADIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  22,55,WE LA JEZALUL-LEDHINE KEFERU FI MIRJETIN MINHU HETTA TE’TIJEHUMU ES-SA’ATU BEGTETEN ‘EW JE’TIJEHUM ‘ADHABU JEWMIN ‘AKIMIN
  22,56,EL-MULKU JEWME’IDHIN LILLAHI JEHKUMU BEJNEHUM FE-EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI FI XHENNATI EN-NA’IMI
  22,57,WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA FE’ULA’IKE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN MUHINUN
  22,58,WEL-LEDHINE HAXHERU FI SEBILI ELLAHI THUMME KUTILU ‘EW MATU LEJERZUKANNEHUMU ELLAHU RIZKÆN HESENÆN WE ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEHUWE HAJRU ER-RAZIKINE
  22,59,LEJUDHILENNEHUM MUDHALÆN JERDEWNEHU WE ‘INNALL-LLAHE LE’ALIMUN HELIMUN
  22,60,DHALIKE WE MEN ‘AKABE BIMITHLI MA ‘UKIBE BIHI THUMME BUGIJE ‘ALEJHI LEJENSURENNEHU ELLAHU ‘INNALL-LLAHE LE’AFUWUN GAFURUN
  22,61,DHALIKE BI’ENNEL-LAHE JULIXHUL-LEJLE FI EN-NEHARI WE JULIXHU EN-NEHARE FIL-LEJLI WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE SEMI’UN BESIRUN
  22,62,DHALIKE BI’ENNEL-LAHE HUWEL-HEKKU WE ‘ENNE MA JED’UNE MIN DUNIHI HUWEL-BATILU WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE HUWEL-’ALIJUL-KEBIRU
  22,63,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FETUSBIHUL-’ERDU MUHDERRETEN ‘INNALL-LLAHE LETIFUN HABIRUN
  22,64,LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEHUWEL-GANIJUL-HEMIDU
  22,65,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE SEHHARE LEKUM MA FIL-’ERDI WEL-FULKE TEXHRI FIL-BEHRI BI’EMRIHI WE JUMSIKU ES-SEMA’E ‘EN TEKA’A ‘ALEL-’ERDI ‘ILLA BI’IDHNIHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE BIN-NASI LERE’UFUN REHIMUN
  22,66,WE HUWEL-LEDHI ‘EHJAKUM THUMME JUMITUKUM THUMME JUHJIKUM ‘INNEL-’INSANE LEKEFURUN
  22,67,LIKULLI ‘UMMETIN XHE’ALNA MENSEKÆN HUM NASIKUHU FELA JUNAZI’UNNEKE FIL-’EMRI WE ED’U ‘ILA RABBIKE ‘INNEKE LE’ALA HUDEN MUSTEKIMIN
  22,68,WE ‘IN XHADELUKE FEKULI ELLAHU ‘A’LEMU BIMA TA’MELUNE
  22,69,ELLAHU JEHKUMU BEJNEKUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FIMA KUNTUM FIHI TEHTELIFUNE
  22,70,‘ELEM TA’LEM ‘ENNEL-LAHE JA’LEMU MA FI ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI ‘INNE DHALIKE FI KITABIN ‘INNE DHALIKE ‘ALA ELLAHI JESIRUN
  22,71,WE JA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LEM JUNEZZIL BIHI SULTANÆN WE MA LEJSE LEHUM BIHI ‘ILMUN WE MA LILDHDHALIMINE MIN NESIRIN
  22,72,WE ‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATUNA BEJJINATIN TA’RIFU FI WUXHUHIL-LEDHINE KEFERUL-MUNKERE JEKADUNE JESTUNE BIEL-LEDHINE JETLUNE ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATINA KUL ‘EFE’UNEBBI’UKUM BISHERRIN MIN DHELIKUMU EN-NARU WE’ADEHALLAHUL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE BI’SEL-MESIRU
  22,73,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU DURIBE METHELUN FASTEMI’U LEHU ‘INNEL-LEDHINE TED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI LEN JEHLUKU DHUBABÆN WE LEWI EXHTEMA’U LEHU WE ‘IN JESLUBHUMU EDH-DHUBABU SHEJ’ÆN LA JESTENKIDHUHU MINHU DA’UFET-TALIBU WEL-METLUBU
  22,74,MA KADERU ELLAHE HEKKA KADRIHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEKAWIJUN ‘AZIZUN
  22,75,ELLAHU JESTEFI MINEL-MELA’IKETI RUSULÆN WE MINE EN-NASI ‘INNALL-LLAHE SEMI’UN BESIRUN
  22,76,JA’LEMU MA BEJNE ‘EJDIHIM WE MA HALFEHUM WE ‘ILA ELLAHI TURXHA’UL-’UMURU
  22,77,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ERKA’U WE ESXHUDU WE A’BUDU REBBEKUM WE EF’ALUL-HAJRE LE’ALLEKUM TUFLIHUNE
  22,78,WE XHAHIDU FI ELLAHI HEKKA XHIHADIHI HUWE EXHTEBAKUM WE MA XHE’ALE ‘ALEJKUM FI ED-DINI MIN HEREXHIN MILLETE ‘EBIKUM ‘IBRAHIME HUWE SEMMAKUMUL-MUSLIMJNE MIN KABLU WE FI HADHA LIJEKUNE ER-RESULU SHEHIDÆN ‘ALEJKUM WE TEKUNU SHUHEDA’E ‘ALA EN-NASI FE’EKIMU ES
  23,1,KAD ‘EFLEHEL-MU’UMINUNE
  23,2,EL-LEDHINE HUM FI SELATIHIM HASHI’UNE
  23,3,WEL-LEDHINE HUM ‘ANIL-LEGWI MU’RIDUNE
  23,4,WEL-LEDHINE HUM LILZZEKÆTI FA’ILUNE
  23,5,WEL-LEDHINE HUM LIFURUXHIHIM HAFIDHUNE
  23,6,‘ILLA ‘ALA ‘EZWAXHIHIM ‘W MA MELEKET ‘EJMANUHUM FE’INNEHUM GAJRU MELUMINE
  23,7,FEMENI EBTEGA WERA’E DHALIKE FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-’ADUNE
  23,8,WEL-LEDHINE HUM LI’MANATIHIM WE ‘AHDIHIM RA’UNE
  23,9,WEL-LEDHINE HUM ‘ALA SELEWATIHIM JUHAFIDHUNE
  23,10,‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-WARITHUNE
  23,11,EL-LEDHINE JERITHUNEL-FIRDEWSE HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  23,12,WE LEKAD HALEKNAL-’INSANE MIN SULALETIN MIN TININ
  23,13,THUMME XHE’ALNAHU NUTFETEN FI KARARIN MEKININ
  23,14,THUMME HALEKNA EN-NUTFETE ‘ALEKATEN FEHALEKNAL-’ALEKATE MUDGATEN FEHALEKNAL-MUDGATE ‘IDHAMÆN FEKESEWNAL-’IDHAME LEHMÆN THUMME ‘ENSHE’NAHU HALKÆN ‘AHARE FETEBAREKEL-LAHU ‘EHSENUL-HALIKINE
  23,15,THUMME ‘INNEKUM BA’DE DHALIKE LEMEJJITUNE
  23,16,THUMME ‘INNEKUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI TUB’ATHUNE
  23,17,WE LEKAD HALEKNA FEWKAKUM SEB’A TERA’IKA WE MA KUNNA ‘ANIL-HALKI GAFILINE
  23,18,WE ‘ENZELNA MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN BIKADERIN FE’ESKENNAHU FIL-’ERDI WE ‘INNA ‘ALA DHEHABIN BIHI LEKADIRUNE
  23,19,FE’ENSHE’NA LEKUM BIHI XHENNATIN MIN NEHILIN WE ‘A’NABIN LEKUM FIHA FEWAKIHU KETHIRETUN WE MINHA TE’KULUNE
  23,20,WE SHEXHERETEN TEHRUXHU MIN TURI SEJNA’E TENBUTU BID-DUHNI WE SIBGIN LIL’AKILINE
  23,21,WE ‘INNE LEKUM FIL-’EN’AMI LA’IBRETEN NUSKIKUM MIMMA FI BUTUNIHA WE LEKUM FIHA MENAFI’U KETHIRETUN WE MINHA TE’KULUNE
  23,22,WE ‘ALEJHA WE ‘ALEL-FULKI TUHMELUNE
  23,23,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA NUHÆN ‘ILA KAWMIHI FEKALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU ‘EFELA TETTEKUNE
  23,24,FEKALEL-MELE’UL-LEDHINE KEFERU MIN KAWMIHI MA HADHA ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUKUM JURIDU ‘EN JETEFEDDELE ‘ALEJKUM WE LEW SHA’EL-LAHU LE’ENZELE MELA’IKETEN MA SEMI’NA BIHEDHA FI ‘ABA’INAL-’EWWELINE
  23,25,‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA REXHULUN BIHI XHINNETUN FETEREBBESU BIHI HETTA HININ
  23,26,KALE RABBI ENSURNI BIMA KEDHDHEBUNI
  23,27,FE’EWHEJNA ‘ILEJHI ‘ENI ESNA’IL-FULKE BI’A’JUNINA WE WEHJINA FE’IDHA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA WE FARET-TENNURU FASLUK FIHA MIN KULLIN ZEWXHEJNI ETHNEJNI WE ‘EHLEKE ‘ILLA MEN SEBEKA ‘ALEJHIL-KAWLU MINHUM WE LA TUHATIBNI FIL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ‘INNEHUM MUGREKUNE
  23,28,FE’IDHA ESTEWEJTE ‘ENTE WE MEN ME’AKE ‘ALEL-FULKI FEKULIL-HEMDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI NEXHXHANA MINEL-KAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  23,29,WE KUL RABBI ‘ENZILNI MUNZELÆN MUBAREKÆN WE ‘ENTE HAJRUL-MUNZILINE
  23,30,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN WE ‘IN KUNNA LEMUBTELINE
  23,31,THUMME ‘ENSHE’NA MIN BA’DIHIM KARNÆN ‘AHARINE
  23,32,FE’ERSELNA FIHIM RESULÆN MINHUM ‘ENI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU ‘EFELA TETTEKUNE
  23,33,WE KALEL-MELE’U MIN KAWMIHIL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE KEDHDHEBU BILIKA’IL-’AHIRETI WE ‘ETREFNAHUM FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA MA HADHA ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUKUM JE’KULU MIMMA TE’KULUNE MINHU WE JESHREBU MIMMA TESHREBUNE
  23,34,WE LE’IN ‘ETA’TUM BESHERÆN MITHLEKUM ‘INNEKUM ‘IDHÆN LEHASIRUNE
  23,35,‘EJA’IDUKUM ‘ENNEKUM ‘IDHA MITTUM WE KUNTUM TURABÆN WE ‘IDHAMÆN ‘ENNEKUM MUHREXHUNE
  23,36,HEJHATE HEJHATE LIMA TU’ADUNE
  23,37,‘IN HIJE ‘ILLA HEJATUNA ED-DUNJA NEMUTU WE NEHJA WE MA NEHNU BIMEB’UTHINE
  23,38,‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA REXHULUN EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN WE MA NEHNU LEHU BIMU’UMININE
  23,39,KALE RABBI ENSURNI BIMA KEDHDHEBUNI
  23,40,KALE ‘AMMA KALILIN LEJUSBIHUNNE NADIMINE
  23,41,FE’EHADHET/HUMU ES-SEJHETU BIL-HEKKI FEXHE’ALNAHUM GUTHA’EN FEBU’DÆN LILKAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  23,42,THUMME ‘ENSHE’NA MIN BA’DIHIM KURUNÆN ‘AHARINE
  23,43,MA TESBIKU MIN ‘UMMETIN ‘EXHELEHA WE MA JESTE’HIRUNE
  23,44,THUMME ‘ERSELNA RUSULENA TETRA KULLE MA XHA’E ‘UMMETEN RESULUHA KEDHDHEBUHU FE’ETBA’NA BA’DEHUM BA’DÆN WE XHE’ALNAHUM ‘EHADITHE FEBU’DÆN LIKAWMIN LA JU’UMINUNE
  23,45,THUMME ‘ERSELNA MUSA WE ‘EHAHU HARUNE BI’AJATINA WE SULTANIN MUBININ
  23,46,‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHI FASTEKBERU WE KANU KAWMÆN ‘ALINE
  23,47,FEKALU ‘ENU’UMINU LIBESHEREJNI MITHLINA WE KAWMUHUMA LENA ‘ABIDUNE
  23,48,FEKEDHDHEBUHUMA FEKANU MINEL-MUHLEKINE
  23,49,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA MUSAL-KITABE LE’ALLEHUM JEHTEDUNE
  23,50,WE XHE’ALNA EBNE MERJEME WE ‘UMMEHU ‘AJETEN WE ‘AWEJNAHUMA ‘ILA REBWETIN DHATI KARARIN WE MA’ININ
  23,51,JA ‘EJJUHA ER-RUSULU KULU MINET-TEJJIBATI WE A’MELU SALIHÆN ‘INNI BIMA TA’MELUNE ‘ALIMUN
  23,52,WE ‘INNE HEDHIHI ‘UMMETUKUM ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN WE ‘ENA REBBUKUM FE ETTEKUNI
  23,53,FETEKATTA’U ‘EMREHUM BEJNEHUM ZUBURÆN KULLU HIZBIN BIMA LEDEJHIM FERIHUNE
  23,54,FEDHERHUM FI GAMRETIHIM HETTA HININ
  23,55,‘EJEHSEBUNE ‘ENNEMA NUMIDDUHUM BIHI MIN MALIN WE BENINE
  23,56,NUSARI’U LEHUM FIL-HAJRATI BEL LA JESH’URUNE
  23,57,‘INNEL-LEDHINE HUM MIN HASHJETI RABBIHIM MUSHFIKUNE
  23,58,WEL-LEDHINE HUM BI’AJATI RABBIHIM JU’UMINUNE
  23,59,WEL-LEDHINE HUM BIREBBIHIM LA JUSHRIKUNE
  23,60,WEL-LEDHINE JU’UTUNE MA ‘ATEW WE KULUBUHUM WE XHILETUN ‘ENNEHUM ‘ILA RABBIHIM RAXHI’UNE
  23,61,‘ULA’IKE JUSARI’UNE FIL-HAJRATI WE HUM LEHA SABIKUNE
  23,62,WE LA NUKELLIFU NEFSÆN ‘ILLA WUS’AHA WE LEDEJNA KITABUN JENTIKU BIL-HEKKI WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUN
  23,63,BEL KULUBUHUM FI GAMRETIN MIN HADHA WE LEHUM ‘A’MALUN MIN DUNI DHALIKE HUM LEHA ‘AMILUNE
  23,64,HETTA ‘IDHA ‘EHADHNA MUTREFIHIM BIL-’ADHABI ‘IDHA HUM JEXH’ERUNE
  23,65,LA TEXH’ERUL-JEWME ‘INNEKUM MINNA LA TUNSERUNE
  23,66,KAD KANET ‘AJATI TUTLA ‘ALEJKUM FEKUNTUM ‘ALA ‘A’KABIKUM TENKISUNE
  23,67,MUSTEKBIRINE BIHI SAMIRÆN TEHXHURUNE
  23,68,‘EFELEM JEDDEBBERUL-KAWLE ‘EM XHA’EHUM MA LEM JE’TI ‘ABA’EHUMUL-’EWWELINE
  23,69,‘EM LEM JA’RIFU RESULEHUM FEHUM LEHU MUNKIRUNE
  23,70,‘EM JEKULUNE BIHI XHINNETUN BEL XHA’EHUM BIL-HEKKI WE ‘EKTHERUHUM LILHEKKI KARIHUNE
  23,71,WE LEWI ETTEBE’AL-HEKKU ‘EHWA’EHUM LEFESEDETI ES-SEMAWATU WEL-’ERDU WE MEN FIHINNE BEL ‘ETEJNAHUM BIDHIKRIHIM FEHUM ‘AN DHIKRIHIM MU’RIDUNE
  23,72,‘EM TES’ELUHUM HARXHÆN FEHARAXHU RABBIKE HAJRUN WE HUWE HAJRU ER-RAZIKINE
  23,73,WE ‘INNEKE LETED’UHUM ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  23,74,WE ‘INNEL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BIL-’AHIRETI ‘ANI ES-SIRATI LENAKIBUNE
  23,75,WE LEW REHIMNAHUM WE KESHEFNA MA BIHIM MIN DURRIN LELEXHXHU FI TUGJANIHIM JA’MEHUNE
  23,76,WE LEKAD ‘EHADHNAHUM BIL-’ADHABI FEMA ESTEKANU LIREBBIHIM WE MA JETEDERRA’UNE
  23,77,HETTA ‘IDHA FETEHNA ‘ALEJHIM BABÆN DHA ‘ADHABIN SHEDIDIN ‘IDHA HUM FIHI MUBLISUNE
  23,78,WE HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ENSHE’E LEKUMU ES-SEM’A WEL-’EBSARE WEL-’EF’IDETE KALILÆN MA TESHKURUNE
  23,79,WE HUWEL-LEDHI DHERE’EKUM FIL-’ERDI WE ‘ILEJHI TUHSHERUNE
  23,80,WE HUWEL-LEDHI JUHJI WE JUMITU WE LEHU EHTILAFUL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  23,81,BEL KALU MITHLE MA KALEL-’EWWELUNE
  23,82,KALU ‘E’IDHA MITNA WE KUNNA TURABÆN WE ‘IDHAMÆN ‘E’INNA LEMEB’UTHUNE
  23,83,LEKAD WU’IDNA NEHNU WE ‘ABA’UUNA HADHA MIN KABLU ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA ‘ESATIRUL-’EWWELINE
  23,84,KUL LIMENIL-’ERDU WE MEN FIHA ‘IN KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  23,85,SEJEKULUNE LILLAHI KUL ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  23,86,KUL MEN REBBU ES-SEMAWATI ES-SEB’I WE REBBUL-’ARSHIL-’ADHIMI
  23,87,SEJEKULUNE LILLAHI KUL ‘EFELA TETTEKUNE
  23,88,KUL MEN BIJEDIHI MELEKUTU KULLI SHEJ’IN WE HUWE JUXHIRU WE LA JUXHARU ‘ALEJHI ‘IN KUNTUM TA’LEMUN
  23,89,SEJEKULUNE LILLAHI KUL FE’ENNA TUSHERUNE
  23,90,BEL ‘ETEJNAHUM BIL-HEKKI WE ‘INNEHUM LEKADHIBUNE
  23,91,MA ETTEHADHEL-LAHU MIN WELEDIN WE MA KANE ME’AHU MIN ‘ILEHIN ‘IDHÆN LEDHEHEBE KULLU ‘ILEHIN BIMA HALEKA WE LE’ALA BA’DUHUM ‘ALA BA’DIN SUBHANEL-LAHI ‘AMMA JESIFUNE
  23,92,‘ALIMIL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETI FETA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  23,93,KUL RABBI ‘IMMA TURIJENNI MA JU’ADUNE
  23,94,REBBI FELA TEXH’ALNI FIL-KAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  23,95,WE ‘INNA ‘ALA ‘EN NURIJEKE MA NA’IDUHUM LEKADIRUNE
  23,96,EDFA’ BI-ETI HIJE ‘EHSENU ES-SEJJI’ETE NEHNU ‘A’LEMU BIMA JESIFUNE
  23,97,WE KUL RABBI ‘A’UDHU BIKE MIN HEMEZATI ESH-SHEJATINI
  23,98,WE ‘A’UDHU BIKE RABBI ‘EN JEHDURUNI
  23,99,HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’E ‘EHEDEHUMUL-MEWTU KALE RABBI ERXHI’UNI
  23,100,LE’ALLI ‘A’MELU SALIHÆN FIMA TEREKTU KELLA ‘INNEHA KELIMETUN HUWE KA’ILUHA WE MIN WERA’IHIM BERZEHUN ‘ILA JEWMI JUB’ATHUNE
  23,101,FE’IDHA NUFIHA FI ES-SURI FELA ‘ENSABE BEJNEHUM JEWME’IDHIN WE LA JETESA’ELUNE
  23,102,FEMEN THEKULET MEWAZINUHU FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-MUFLIHUNE
  23,103,WE MEN HAFFET MEWAZINUHU FE’ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE HASIRU ‘ENFUSEHUM FI XHEHENNEME HALIDUNE
  23,104,TELFEHU WUXHUHEHUMU EN-NARU WE HUM FIHA KALIHUNE
  23,105,‘ELEM TEKUN ‘AJATI TUTLA ‘ALEJKUM FEKUNTUM BIHA TUKEDHDHIBUNE
  23,106,KALU REBBENA GALEBET ‘ALEJNA SHIKWETUNA WE KUNNA KAWMÆN DALLINE
  23,107,REBBENA ‘EHRIXHNA MINHA FE’IN ‘UDNA FE’INNA DHALIMUNE
  23,108,KALE EHSE’U FIHA WE LA TUKELLIMUNI
  23,109,‘INNEHU KANE FERIKUN MIN ‘IBADI JEKULUNE REBBENA ‘AMENNA FAGFIR LENA WE ERHEMNA WE ‘ENTE HAJRU ER-RAHIMINE
  23,110,FATTEHADHTUMUHUM SIHRIJÆN HETTA ‘ENSEWKUM DHIKRI WE KUNTUM MINHUM TEDHEKUNE
  23,111,‘INNI XHEZEJTUHUMUL-JEWME BIMA SEBERU ‘ENNEHUM HUMUL-FA’IZUNE
  23,112,KALE KEM LEBITHTUM FIL-’ERDI ‘ADEDE SININE
  23,113,KALU LEBITHNA JEWMÆN ‘EW BA’DE JEWMIN FAS’ELIL-’ADDINE
  23,114,KALE ‘IN LEBITHTUM ‘ILLA KALILÆN LEW ‘ENNEKUM KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  23,115,‘EFEHESIBTUM ‘ENNEMA HALEKNAKUM ‘ABETHÆN WE ‘ENNEKUM ‘ILEJNA LA TURXHA’UNE
  23,116,FETA’ALALLAHUL-MELIKUL-HEKKU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE REBBUL-’ARSHIL-KERIMI
  23,117,WE MEN JED’U ME’A ELLAHI ‘ILEHÆN ‘AHARE LA BURHANE LEHU BIHI FE’INNEMA HISABUHU ‘INDE RABBIHI ‘INNEHU LA JUFLIHUL-KAFIRUNE
  23,118,WE KUL RABBI EGFIR WE ERHEM WE ‘ENTE HAJRU ER-RAHIMINE
  24,1,SURETUN ‘ENZELNAHA WE FEREDNAHA WE ‘ENZELNA FIHA ‘AJATIN BEJJINATIN LE’ALLEKUM TEDHEKKERUNE
  24,2,EZ-ZANIJETU WE EZ-ZANI FAXHLIDU KULLE WAHIDIN MINHUMA MIA’ETE XHELDETIN WE LA TE’HUDHKUM BIHIMA RE’FETUN FI DINI ELLAHI ‘IN KUNTUM TU’UMINUNE BILLAHI WEL-JEWMIL-’AHIRI WE LIESH/HED ‘ADHABEHUMA TA’IFETUN MINEL-MU’UMININE
  24,3,EZ-ZANI LA JENKIHU ‘ILLA ZANIJETEN ‘EW MUSHRIKETEN WE EZ-ZANIJETU LA JENKIHUHA ‘ILLA ZANIN ‘EW MUSHRIKUN WE HURRIME DHALIKE ‘ALEL-MU’UMININE
  24,4,WEL-LEDHINE JERMUNEL-MUHSENATI THUMME LEM JE’TU BI’ERBE’ATI SHUHEDA’E FAXHLIDUHUM THEMANINE XHELDETEN WE LA TEKBELU LEHUM SHEHADETEN ‘EBEDÆN WE ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-FASIKUNE
  24,5,‘ILLAL-LEDHINE TABU MIN BA’DI DHALIKE WE ‘ESLEHU FE’INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  24,6,WEL-LEDHINE JERMUNE ‘EZWAXHEHUM WE LEM JEKUN LEHUM SHUHEDA’U ‘ILLA ‘ENFUSUHUM FESHEHADETU ‘EHEDIHIM ‘ERBA’U SHEHADATIN BILLAHI ‘INNEHU LEMINE ES-SADIKINE
  24,7,WEL-HAMISETU ‘ENNE LA’NETEL-LAHI ‘ALEJHI ‘IN KANE MINEL-KADHIBINE
  24,8,WE JEDRE’U ‘ANHAL-’ADHABE ‘EN TESH/HEDE ‘ERBE’A SHEHADATIN BILLAHI ‘INNEHU LEMINEL-KADHIBINE
  24,9,WEL-HAMISETE ‘ENNE GADEBEL-LAHI ‘ALEJHA ‘IN KANE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  24,10,WE LEWLA FEDLU ELLAHI ‘ALEJKUM WE REHMETUHU WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE TEWWABUN HEKIMUN
  24,11,‘INNEL-LEDHINE XHA’U BIL-’IFKI ‘USBETUN MINKUM LA TEHSEBUHU SHERRÆN LEKUM BEL HUWE HAJRUN LEKUM LIKULLI EMRI’IN MINHUM MA EKTESEBE MINEL-’ITHMI WEL-LEDHI TEWELLA KIBREHU MINHUM LEHU ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  24,12,LEWLA ‘IDH SEMI’TUMUHU DHENNEL-MU’UMINUNE WEL-MU’UMINATU BI’ENFUSIHIM HAJRÆN WE KALU HADHA ‘IFKUN MUBINUN
  24,13,LEWLA XHA’U ‘ALEJHI BI’ERBE’ATI SHUHEDA’E FE’IDH LEM JE’TU BISH-SHUHEDA’I FE’ULA’IKE ‘INDEL-LAHI HUMUL-KADHIBUNE
  24,14,WE LEWLA FEDLU ELLAHI ‘ALEJKUM WE REHMETUHU FI ED-DUNJA WEL-’AHIRETI LEMESSEKUM FI MA ‘EFEDTUM FIHI ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  24,15,‘IDH TELEKKAWNEHU BI’ELSINETIKUM WE TEKULUNE BI’EFWAHIKUM MA LEJSE LEKUM BIHI ‘ILMUN WE TEHSEBUNEHU HEJJINÆN WE HUWE ‘INDEL-LAHI ‘ADHIMUN
  24,16,WE LEWLA ‘IDH SEMI’TUMUHU KULTUM MA JEKUNU LENA ‘EN NETEKELLEME BIHEDHA SUBHANEKE HADHA BUHTANUN ‘ADHIMUN
  24,17,JA’IDHUKUMU ELLAHU ‘EN TA’UDU LIMITHLIHI ‘EBEDÆN ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE
  24,18,WE JUBEJJINU ELLAHU LEKUMUL-’AJATI WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN HEKIMUN
  24,19,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JUHIBBUNE ‘EN TESHI’AL-FAHISHETU FIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN FI ED-DUNJA WEL-’AHIRETI WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU WE ‘ENTUM LA TA’LEMUNE
  24,20,WE LEWLA FEDLU ELLAHI ‘ALEJKUM WE REHMETUHU WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE RE’UFUN REHIM
  24,21,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TETTEBI’U HUTUWATI ESH-SHEJTANI WE MEN JETTEBI’ HUTUWATI ESH-SHEJTANI FE’INNEHU JE’MURU BIL-FEHSHA’I WEL-MUNKERI WE LEWLA FEDLU ELLAHI ‘ALEJKUM WE REHMETUHU MA ZEKA MINKUM MIN ‘EHEDIN ‘EBEDÆN WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE JUZEKKI MEN JE
  24,22,WE LA JE’TELI ‘ULUL-FEDLI MINKUM WE ES-SE’ATI ‘EN JU’UTU ‘ULIL-KURBA WEL-MESAKINE WEL-MUHAXHIRINE FI SEBILI ELLAHI WE LIA’FU WE LIESFEHU ‘ELA TUHIBBUNE ‘EN JEGFIREL-LAHU LEKUM WEL-LAHU GAFURUN REHIMUN
  24,23,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JERMUNEL-MUHSENATIL-GAFILATIL-MU’UMINATI LU’INU FI ED-DUNJA WEL-’AHIRETI WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  24,24,JEWME TESH/HEDU ‘ALEJHIM ‘ELSINETUHUM WE ‘EJDIHIM WE ‘ERXHULUHUM BIMA KANU JA’MELUNE
  24,25,JEWME’IDHIN JUWEFFIHIMU ELLAHU DINEHUMUL-HEKKA WE JA’LEMUNE ‘ENNEL-LAHE HUWEL-HEKKUL-MUBINU
  24,26,EL-HABITHATU LILHABITHINE WEL-HABITHUNE LILHABITHATI WET-TEJJIBATU LILTTEJJIBINE WET-TEJJIBUNE LILTTEJJIBATI ‘ULA’IKE MUBERRE’UNE MIMMA JEKULUNE LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE RIZKUN KERIMUN
  24,27,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TEDHULU BUJUTÆN GAJRE BUJUTIKUM HETTA TESTE’NISU WE TUSELLIMU ‘ALA ‘EHLIHA DHALIKUM HAJRUN LEKUM LE’ALLEKUM TEDHEKKERUNE
  24,28,FE’IN LEM TEXHIDU FIHA ‘EHEDÆN FELA TEDHULUHA HETTA JU’UDHENE LEKUM WE ‘IN KILE LEKUM ERXHI’U FARXHI’U HUWE ‘EZKA LEKUM WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE ‘ALIMUN
  24,29,LEJSE ‘ALEJKUM XHUNAHUN ‘EN TEDHULU BUJUTÆN GAJRE MESKUNETIN FIHA META’UN LEKUM WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU MA TUBDUNE WE MA TEKTUMUNE
  24,30,KUL LILMU’UMININE JEGUDDU MIN ‘EBSARIHIM WE JEHFEDHU FURUXHEHUM DHALIKE ‘EZKA LEHUM ‘INNALL-LLAHE HABIRUN BIMA JESNA’UNE
  24,31,WE KUL LILMU’UMINATI JEGDUDNE MIN ‘EBSARIHINNE WE JEHFEDHNE FURUXHEHUNNE WE LA JUBDINE ZINETEHUNNE ‘ILLA MA DHEHERE MINHA WE LIEDRIBNE BIHUMURIHINNE ‘ALA XHUJUBIHINNE WE LA JUBDINE ZINETEHUNNE ‘ILLA LIBU’ULETIHINNE ‘EW ‘ABA’IHINNE ‘EW ‘ABA’I BU’ULETIHINNE
  24,32,WE ‘ENKIHUL-’EJAMA MINKUM WE ES-SALIHINE MIN ‘IBADIKUM WE ‘IMA’IKUM ‘IN JEKUNU FUKARA’E JUGNIHIMU ELLAHU MIN FEDLIHI WEL-LAHU WASI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  24,33,WE LIESTA’FIFIL-LEDHINE LA JEXHIDUNE NIKAHÆN HETTA JUGNIJEHUMU ELLAHU MIN FEDLIHI WEL-LEDHINE JEBTEGUNEL-KITABE MIMMA MELEKET ‘EJMANUKUM FEKATIBUHUM ‘IN ‘ALIMTUM FIHIM HAJRÆN WE ‘ATUHUM MIN MALI ELLAHIL-LEDHI ‘ATAKUM WE LA TUKRIHU FETEJATIKUM ‘ALEL-BIGA’I
  24,34,WE LEKAD ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKUM ‘AJATIN MUBEJJINATIN WE METHELÆN MINEL-LEDHINE HALEW MIN KABLIKUM WE MEW’IDHETEN LILMUTTEKINE
  24,35,ELLAHU NURU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI METHELU NURIHI KEMISHKÆTIN FIHA MISBAHUNL-MISBAHU FI ZUXHAXHETIN EZ-ZUXHAXHETU KE’ENNEHA KEWKEBUN DURRIJUN JUKADU MIN SHEXHERETIN MUBAREKETIN ZEJTUNIETIN LA SHERKIJETIN WE LA GARBIJETIN JEKADU ZEJTUHA JUDI’U WE LEW LEM TE
  24,36,FI BUJUTIN ‘EDHINEL-LAHU ‘EN TURFE’A WE JUDHKERE FIHA ESMUHU JUSEBBIHU LEHU FIHA BIL-GUDUWI WEL-’ASALI
  24,37,RIXHALUN LA TULHIHIM TIXHARETUN WE LA BEJ’UN ‘AN DHIKRI ELLAHI WE ‘IKAMI ES-SELÆTI WE ‘ITA’I EZ-ZEKÆTI JEHAFUNE JEWMÆN TETEKALLEBU FIHIL-KULUBU WEL-’EBSARU
  24,38,LIJEXHZIJEHUMU ELLAHU ‘EHSENE MA ‘AMILU WE JEZIDEHUM MIN FEDLIHI WEL-LAHU JERZUKU MEN JESHA’U BIGAJRI HISABIN
  24,39,WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘A’MALUHUM KESERABIN BIKI’ATIN JEHSEBUHU EDH-DHEM’ANU MA’EN HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’EHU LEM JEXHID/HU SHEJ’ÆN WE WEXHEDEL-LAHE ‘INDEHU FEWEFFAHU HISABEHU WEL-LAHU SERI’UL-HISABI
  24,40,‘EW KEDHULUMATIN FI BEHRIN LUXHXHIJIN JEGSHAHU MEWXHUN MIN FEWKIHI MEWXHUN MIN FEWKIHI SEHABUN DHULUMATUN BA’DUHA FEWKA BA’DIN ‘IDHA ‘EHREXHE JEDEHU LEM JEKED JERAHA WE MEN LEM JEXH’ALI ELLAHU LEHU NURÆN FEMA LEHU MIN NURIN
  24,41,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE JUSEBBIHU LEHU MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WET-TEJRU SAFFATIN KULLUN KAD ‘ALIME SELATEHU WE TESBIHEHU WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN BIMA JEF’ALUNE
  24,42,WE LILLEHI MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE ‘ILA ELLAHIL-MESIRU
  24,43,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE JUZXHI SEHABÆN THUMME JU’UELLIFU BEJNEHU THUMME JEXH’ALUHU RUKAMÆN FETERAL-WEDKA JEHRUXHU MIN HILALIHI WE JUNEZZILU MINE ES-SEMA’I MIN XHIBALIN FIHA MIN BEREDIN FEJUSIBU BIHI MEN JESHA’U WE JESRIFUHU ‘AN MEN JESHA’U JEKADU SENA BERK
  24,44,JUKALLIBU ELLAHUL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHARE ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LA’IBRETEN LI’WLIL-’EBSARI
  24,45,WEL-LAHU HALEKA KULLE DABBETIN MIN MA’IN FEMINHUM MEN JEMSHI ‘ALA BETNIHI WE MINHUM MEN JEMSHI ‘ALA RIXHLEJNI WE MINHUM MEN JEMSHI ‘ALA ‘ERBA’IN JEHLUKU ELLAHU MA JESHA’U ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  24,46,LEKAD ‘ENZELNA ‘AJATIN MUBEJJINATIN WEL-LAHU JEHDI MEN JESHA’U ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  24,47,WE JEKULUNE ‘AMENNA BILLAHI WE BIR-RESULI WE ‘ETA’NA THUMME JETEWELLA FERIKUN MINHUM MIN BA’DI DHALIKE WE MA ‘ULA’IKE BIL-MU’UMININE
  24,48,WE ‘IDHA DU’U ‘ILA ELLAHI WE RESULIHI LIJEHKUME BEJNEHUM ‘IDHA FERIKUN MINHUM MU’RIDUNE
  24,49,WE ‘IN JEKUN LEHUMUL-HEKKU JE’TU ‘ILEJHI MUDH’ININE
  24,50,‘EFI KULUBIHIM MEREDUN ‘EM ERTABU ‘EM JEHAFUNE ‘EN JEHIFEL-LAHU ‘ALEJHIM WE RESULUHU BEL ‘ULA’IKE HUMU EDH-DHALIMUN
  24,51,‘INNEMA KANE KAWLEL-MU’UMININE ‘IDHA DU’U ‘ILA ELLAHI WE RESULIHI LIJEHKUME BEJNEHUM ‘EN JEKULU SEMI’NA WE ‘ETA’NA WE ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-MUFLIHUNE
  24,52,WE MEN JUTI’I ELLAHE WE RESULEHU WE JEHSHEL-LAHE WE JETTEKHI FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-FA’IZUNE
  24,53,WE ‘EKSEMU BILLAHI XHEHDE ‘EJMANIHIM LE’IN ‘EMERTEHUM LEJEHRUXHUNNE KUL LA TUKSIMU TA’ATUN MA’RUFETUN ‘INNALL-LLAHE HABIRUN BIMA TA’MELUNE
  24,54,KUL ‘ETI’U ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’U ER-RESULE FE’IN TEWELLEW FE’INNEMA ‘ALEJHI MA HUMMILE WE ‘ALEJKUM MA HUMMILTUM WE ‘IN TUTI’UHU TEHTEDU WE MA ‘ALA ER-RESULI ‘ILLAL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  24,55,WE’ADEL-LAHUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU MINKUM WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LEJESTEHLIFENNEHUM FIL-’ERDI KEMA ESTEHLEFEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE LEJUMEKKINENNE LEHUM DINEHUMUL-LEDHI ERTEDA LEHUM WE LEJUBEDDILENNEHUM MIN BA’DI HAWFIHIM ‘EMNÆN JA’BUDUNENI LA JUSHRIKUNE BI SH
  24,56,WE ‘EKIMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ATU EZ-ZEKÆTE WE ‘ETI’U ER-RESULE LE’ALLEKUM TURHEMUNE
  24,57,LA TEHSEBENNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU MU’XHIZINE FIL-’ERDI WE ME’WAHUMU EN-NARU WE LEBI’SEL-MESIRU
  24,58,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LIJESTE’DHINKUMUL-LEDHINE MELEKET ‘EJMANUKUM WEL-LEDHINE LEM JEBLUGUL-HULUME MINKUM THELATHE MERRATIN MIN KABLI SELÆTIL-FEXHRI WE HINE TEDA’UNE THIJA BEKUM MINE EDH-DHEHIRETI WE MIN BA’DI SELÆTIL-’ISHA’I THELATHU ‘AWRATIN LEKUM
  24,59,WE ‘IDHA BELEGAL-’ETFALU MINKUMUL-HULUME FELJESTE’DHINU KEMA ESTE’DHENEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM KEDHALIKE JUBEJJINU ELLAHU LEKUM ‘AJATIHI WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN HEKIMUN
  24,60,WEL-KAWA’IDU MINE EN-NISA’L-LATI LA JERXHUNE NIKAHÆN FELEJSE ‘ALEJHINNE XHUNAHUN ‘EN JEDA’NE THIJABEHUNNE GAJRE MUTEBERRIXHATIN BIZINETIN WE ‘EN JESTA’FIFNE HAJRUN LEHUNNE WEL-LAHU SEMI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  24,61,LEJSE ‘ALEL-’A’MA HEREXHUN WE LA ‘ALEL-’A’REXHI HEREXHUN WE LA ‘ALEL-MERIDI HEREXHUN WE LA ‘ALA ‘ENFUSIKUM ‘EN TE’KULU MIN BUJUTIKUM ‘EW BUJUTI ‘ABA’IKUM ‘EW BUJUTI ‘UMMEHATIKUM ‘EW BUJUTI ‘IHWANIKUM ‘EW BUJUTI ‘EHAWATIKUM ‘EW BUJUTI ‘A’MAMIKUM ‘EW BUJUTI
  24,62,‘INNEMAL-MU’UMINUNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU BILLAHI WE RESULIHI WE ‘IDHA KANU ME’AHU ‘ALA ‘EMRIN XHAMI’IN LEM JEDH/HEBU HETTA JESTE’DHINUHU ‘INNEL-LEDHINE JESTE’DHINUNEKE ‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE JU’UMINUNE BILLAHI WE RESULIHI FE’IDHA ESTE’DHENUKE LIBA’DI SHE’NIHIM FE’D
  24,63,LA TEXH’ALU DU’A’E ER-RESULI BEJNEKUM KEDU’A’I BA’DIKUM BA’DÆN KAD JA’LEMU ELLAHUL-LEDHINE JETESELLELUNE MINKUM LIWADHÆN FELJEHDHERIL-LEDHINE JUHALIFUNE ‘AN ‘EMRIHI ‘EN TUSIBEHUM FITNETUN ‘EW JUSIBEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  24,64,‘ELA ‘INNE LILLAHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI KAD JA’LEMU MA ‘ENTUM ‘ALEJHI WE JEWME JURXHA’UNE ‘ILEJHI FEJUNEBBI’UHUM BIMA ‘AMILU WEL-LAHU BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMUN
  25,1,TEBAREKEL-LEDHI NEZZELEL-FURKANE ‘ALA ‘ABDIHI LIJEKUNE LIL’ALEMINE NEDHIRÆN
  25,2,EL-LEDHI LEHU MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE LEM JETTEHIDH WELEDÆN WE LEM JEKUN LEHU SHERIKUN FIL-MULKI WE HALEKA KULLE SHEJ’IN FEKADDEREHU TEKDIRÆN
  25,3,WE ETTEHADHU MIN DUNIHI ‘ALIHETEN LA JEHLUKUNE SHEJ’ÆN WE HUM JUHLEKUNE WE LA JEMLIKUNE LI’NFUSIHIM DERRÆN WE LA NEF’ÆN WE LA JEMLIKUNE MEWTÆN WE LA HEJÆTEN WE LA NUSHURÆN
  25,4,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA ‘IFKUN EFTERAHU WE ‘A’ANEHU ‘ALEJHI KAWMUN ‘AHARUNE FEKAD XHA’U DHULMÆN WE ZURÆN
  25,5,WE KALU ‘ESATIRUL-’EWWELINE EKTETEBEHA FEHIJE TUMLA ‘ALEJHI BUKRETEN WE ‘ESILÆN
  25,6,KUL ‘ENZELEHUL-LEDHI JA’LEMU ES-SIRRE FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘INNEHU KANE GAFURÆN REHIMÆN
  25,7,WE KALU MALI HADHA ER-RESULI JE’KULUT-TA’AME WE JEMSHI FIL-’ESWAKI LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJHI MELEKUN FEJEKUNE ME’AHU NEDHIRÆN
  25,8,‘EW JULKA ‘ILEJHI KENZUN ‘EW TEKUNU LEHU XHENNETUN JE’KULU MINHA WE KALE EDH-DHALIMUNE ‘IN TETTEBI’UNE ‘ILLA REXHULÆN MESHURÆN
  25,9,ENDHUR KEJFE DEREBU LEKEL-’EMTHALE FEDELLU FELA JESTETI’UNE SEBILÆN
  25,10,TEBAREKEL-LEDHI ‘IN SHA’E XHE’ALE LEKE HAJRÆN MIN DHALIKE XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU WE JEXH’AL LEKE KUSURÆN
  25,11,BEL KEDHDHEBU BIS-SA’ATI WE ‘A’TEDNA LIMEN KEDHDHEBE BIS-SA’ATI SA’IRÆN
  25,12,‘IDHA RE’ET/HUM MIN MEKANIN BA’IDIN SEMI’U LEHA TEGAJJUDHÆN WE ZEFIRÆN
  25,13,WE ‘IDHA ‘ULKU MINHA MEKANÆN DEJJIKÆN MUKARRENINE DE’AW HUNALIKE THUBURÆN
  25,14,LA TED’UL-JEWME THUBURÆN WAHIDÆN WE ED’U THUBURÆN KETHIRÆN
  25,15,KUL ‘EDHELIKE HAJRUN ‘EM XHENNETUL-HULDI ELLETI WU’IDEL-MUTTEKUNE KANET LEHUM XHEZA’EN WE MESIRÆN
  25,16,LEHUM FIHA MA JESHA’UNE HALIDINE KANE ‘ALA RABBIKE WA’DÆN MES’ULÆN
  25,17,WE JEWME JEHSHURUHUM WE MA JA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI FEJEKULU ‘E’ENTUM ‘EDLELTUM ‘IBADI HA’UULA’ ‘EM HUM DELLU ES-SEBILE
  25,18,KALU SUBHANEKE MA KANE JENBEGI LENA ‘EN NETTEHIDHE MIN DUNIKE MIN ‘EWLIJA’E WE LEKIN METTA’TEHUM WE ‘ABA’EHUM HETTA NESU EDH-DHIKRE WE KANU KAWMÆN BURÆN
  25,19,FEKAD KEDHDHEBUKUM BIMA TEKULUNE FEMA TESTETI’UNE SERFÆN WE LA NESRÆN WE MEN JEDHLIM MINKUM NUDHIKHU ‘ADHABÆN KEBIRÆN
  25,20,WE MA ‘ERSELNA KABLEKE MINEL-MURSELINE ‘ILLA ‘INNEHUM LEJE’KULUNET-TA’AME WE JEMSHUNE FIL-’ESWAKI WE XHE’ALNA BA’DEKUM LIBA’DIN FITNETEN ‘ETESBIRUNE WE KANE REBBUKE BESIRÆN
  25,21,WE KALEL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJNAL-MELA’IKETU ‘EW NERA REBBENA LEKADI ESTEKBERU FI ‘ENFUSIHIM WE ‘ATEW ‘UTUWÆN KEBIRÆN
  25,22,JEWME JEREWNEL-MELA’IKETE LA BUSHRA JEWME’IDHIN LILMUXHRIMINE WE JEKULUNE HIXHRÆN MEHXHURÆN
  25,23,WE KADIMNA ‘ILA MA ‘AMILU MIN ‘AMELIN FEXHE’ALNAHU HEBA’EN MENTHURÆN
  25,24,‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI JEWME’IDHIN HAJRUN MUSTEKARRÆN WE ‘EHSENU MEKILÆN
  25,25,WE JEWME TESHEKKAKU ES-SEMA’U BIL-GAMAMI WE NUZZILEL-MELA’IKETU TENZILÆN
  25,26,EL-MULKU JEWME’IDHINL-HEKKU LILRREHMENI WE KANE JEWMÆN ‘ALEL-KAFIRINE ‘ASIRÆN
  25,27,WE JEWME JE’ADDU EDH-DHALIMU ‘ALA JEDEJHI JEKULU JA LEJTENI ETTEHADHTU ME’A ER-RESULI SEBILÆN
  25,28,JA WEJLETI LEJTENI LEM ‘ETTEHIDH FULANÆN HALILÆN
  25,29,LEKAD ‘EDELLENI ‘ANI EDH-DHIKRI BA’DE ‘IDH XHA’ENI WE KANE ESH-SHEJTANU LIL’INSANI HADHULÆN
  25,30,WE KALE ER-RESULU JA RABBI ‘INNE KAWMI ETTEHADHU HADHAL-KUR’ANE MEHXHURÆN
  25,31,WE KEDHELIKE XHE’ALNA LIKULLI NEBIJIN ‘ADUWÆN MINEL-MUXHRIMINE WE KEFA BIREBBIKE HADIÆN WE NESIRÆN
  25,32,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEWLA NUZZILE ‘ALEJHIL-KUR’ANU XHUMLETEN WAHIDETEN KEDHALIKE LINUTHEBBITE BIHI FU’UADEKE WE RETTELNAHU TERTILÆN
  25,33,WE LA JE’TUNEKE BIMETHELIN ‘ILLA XHI’NAKE BIL-HEKKI WE ‘EHSENE TEFSIRÆN
  25,34,EL-LEDHINE JUHSHERUNE ‘ALA WUXHUHIHIM ‘ILA XHEHENNEME ‘ULA’IKE SHERRUN MEKANÆN WE ‘EDELLU SEBILÆN
  25,35,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA MUSAL-KITABE WE XHE’ALNA ME’AHU ‘EHAHU HARUNE WEZIRÆN
  25,36,FEKULNA EDH/HEBA ‘ILAL-KAWMIL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA FEDEMMERNAHUM TEDMIRÆN
  25,37,WE KAWME NUHIN LEMMA KEDHDHEBU ER-RUSULE ‘EGREKNAHUM WE XHE’ALNAHUM LILNNASI ‘AJETEN WE ‘A’TEDNA LILDHDHALIMINE ‘ADHABÆN ‘ELIMÆN
  25,38,WE ‘ADÆN WE THEMUDE WE ‘ESHABE ER-RESSI WE KURUNÆN BEJNE DHALIKE KETHIRÆN
  25,39,WE KULLÆN DEREBNA LEHUL-’EMTHALE WE KULLÆN TEBBERNA TETBIRÆN
  25,40,WE LEKAD ‘ETEW ‘ALEL-KARJETI ELLETI ‘UMTIRET METERE ES-SEW’I ‘EFELEM JEKUNU JEREWNEHA BEL KANU LA JERXHUNE NUSHURÆN
  25,41,WE ‘IDHA R’EWKE ‘IN JETTEHIDHUNEKE ‘ILLA HUZUEN ‘EHEDHAL-LEDHI BE’ATHEL-LAHU RESULÆN
  25,42,‘IN KADE LEJUDILLUNA ‘AN ‘ALIHETINA LEWLA ‘EN SEBERNA ‘ALEJHA WE SEWFE JA’LEMUNE HINE JEREWNEL-’ADHABE MEN ‘EDELLU SEBILÆN
  25,43,‘ERE’EJTE MENI ETTEHADHE ‘ILEHEHU HEWAHU ‘EFE’ENTE TEKUNU ‘ALEJHI WE KILÆN
  25,44,‘EM TEHSEBU ‘ENNE ‘EKTHEREHUM JESMA’UNE ‘EW JA’KILUNE ‘IN HUM ‘ILLA KAL’EN’AM BEL HUM ‘EDELLU SEBILÆN
  25,45,‘ELEM TERA ‘ILA RABBIKE KEJFE MEDDE EDH-DHILLE WE LEW SHA’E LEXHE’ALEHU SAKINÆN THUMME XHE’ALNA ESH-SHEMSE ‘ALEJHI DELILÆN
  25,46,THUMME KABEDNAHU ‘ILEJNA KABDÆN JESIRÆN
  25,47,WE HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-LEJLE LIBASÆN WE EN-NEWME SUBATÆN WE XHE’ALE EN-NEHARE NUSHURÆN
  25,48,WE HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ERSELE ER-RIJAHE BUSHRÆN BEJNE JEDEJ REHMETIHI WE ‘ENZELNA MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN TEHURÆN
  25,49,LINUHJIJE BIHI BELDETEN MEJTÆN WE NUSKIJEHU MIMMA HALEKNA ‘EN’AMÆN WE ‘ENASIJE KETHIRÆN
  25,50,WE LEKAD SERREFNAHU BEJNEHUM LIJEDHDHEKKERU FE’EBA ‘EKTHERU EN-NASI ‘ILLA KUFURÆN
  25,51,WE LEW SHI’NA LEBE’ATHNA FI KULLI KARJETIN NEDHIRÆN
  25,52,FELA TUTI’IL-KAFIRINE WE XHAHID/HUM BIHI XHIHADÆN KEBIRÆN
  25,53,WE HUWEL-LEDHI MEREXHEL-BEHREJNI HADHA ‘ADHBUN FURATUN WE HEDHA MILHUN ‘UXHAXHUN WE XHE’ALE BEJNEHUMA BERZEHÆN WE HIXHRÆN MEHXHURÆN
  25,54,WE HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKA MINEL-MA’I BESHERÆN FEXHE’ALEHU NESEBÆN WE SIHRÆN WE KANE REBBUKE KADIRÆN
  25,55,WE JA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JENFA’UHUM WE LA JEDURRUHUM WE KANEL-KAFIRU ‘ALA RABBIHI DHEHIRÆN
  25,56,WE MA ‘ERSELNAKE ‘ILLA MUBESHSHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN
  25,57,KUL MA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘ILLA MEN SHA’E ‘EN JETTEHIDHE ‘ILA RABBIHI SEBILÆN
  25,58,WE TEWEKKEL ‘ALEL-HEJJIL-LEDHI LA JEMUTU WE SEBBIH BIHEMDIHI WE KEFA BIHI BIDHUNUBI ‘IBADIHI HABIRÆN
  25,59,EL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE MA BEJNEHUMA FI SITTETI ‘EJJAMIN THUMME ESTEWA ‘ALEL-’ARSHI ER-REHMANU FAS’EL BIHI HABIRÆN
  25,60,WE ‘IDHA KILE LEHUM ESXHUDU LILRREHMENI KALU WE MA ER-REHMANU ‘ENESXHUDU LIMA TE’MURUNA WE ZADEHUM NUFURÆN
  25,61,TEBAREKEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE FI ES-SEMA’I BURUXHÆN WE XHE’ALE FIHA SIRAXHÆN WE KAMERÆN MUNIRÆN
  25,62,WE HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALEL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHARE HILFETEN LIMEN ‘ERADE ‘EN JEDHDHEKKERE ‘EW ‘ERADE SHUKURÆN
  25,63,WE ‘IBADU ER-REHMANIL-LEDHINE JEMSHUNE ‘ALEL-’ERDI HEWNÆN WE ‘IDHA HATEBEHUMUL-XHAHILUNE KALU SELAMÆN
  25,64,WEL-LEDHINE JEBITUNE LIREBBIHIM SUXHXHEDÆN WE KIJAMÆN
  25,65,WEL-LEDHINE JEKULUNE REBBENA ESRIF ‘ANNA ‘ADHABE XHEHENNEME ‘INNE ‘ADHABEHA KANE GARAMÆN
  25,66,‘INNEHA SA’ET MUSTEKARRÆN WE MUKAMÆN
  25,67,WEL-LEDHINE ‘IDHA ‘ENFEKU LEM JUSRIFU WE LEM JEKTURU WE KANE BEJNE DHALIKE KAWAMÆN
  25,68,WEL-LEDHINE LA JED’UNE ME’A ELLAHI ‘ILEHÆN ‘AHARE WE LA JEKTULUNE EN-NEFSEL-LETI HERREMEL-LAHU ‘ILLA BIL-HEKKI WE LA JEZNUNE WE MEN JEF’AL DHALIKE JELKA ‘ETHAMÆN
  25,69,JUDA’AF LEHUL-’ADHABU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE JEHLUD FIHI MUHANÆN
  25,70,‘ILLA MEN TABE WE ‘AMENE WE ‘AMILE ‘AMELÆN SALIHÆN FE’ULA’IKE JUBEDDILU ELLAHU SEJJI’ATIHIM HESENATIN WE KANEL-LAHU GAFURÆN REHIMÆN
  25,71,WE MEN TABE WE ‘AMILE SALIHÆN FE’INNEHU JETUBU ‘ILA ELLAHI METABÆN
  25,72,WEL-LEDHINE LA JESH/HEDUNE EZ-ZURE WE ‘IDHA MERRU BIL-LEGWI MERRU KIRAMÆN
  25,73,WEL-LEDHINE ‘IDHA DHUKKIRU BI’AJATI RABBIHIM LEM JEHIRRU ‘ALEJHA SUMMÆN WE ‘UMJANÆN
  25,74,WEL-LEDHINE JEKULUNE REBBENA HEB LENA MIN ‘EZWAXHINA WE DHURRIJATINA KURRETE ‘A’JUNIN WE EXH’ALNA LILMUTTEKINE ‘IMAMÆN
  25,75,‘ULA’IKE JUXHZEWNEL-GURFETE BIMA SEBERU WE JULEKKAWNE FIHA TEHIJETEN WE SELAMÆN
  25,76,HALIDINE FIHA HESUNET MUSTEKARRÆN WE MUKAMÆN
  25,77,KUL MA JA’BE’U BIKUM RABBI LEWLA DU’A’UUKUM FEKAD KEDHDHEBTUM FESEWFE JEKUNU LIZAMÆN